CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 9, 1967, pg. 15, reads: "ULG Boat Ride - For the past few years, one of the social highlights of the season has been a boat ride sponsored by the Urban League Guild of Pittsburgh. This year was no exception and a happy throng was on hand for the event held recently."
TitMainTitle: Women and men walking on gang plank to riverboat, for Urban League Guild of Pittsburgh's annual boat ride, with Fulton Building in background, Downtown
